; CraterGap kill zone — NGKs Crater Wardens V1 (Godot 4)
; Phase 3: Hazards
;
; Area2D kill zone placed underneath a terrain gap.
; Placed 70 px below ground surface (surface Y=550, kill zone Y=620).
; Default shape 440 x 60 — covers short (260px) and long (400px) gaps.
; Place two instances: one under each gap in test_lane.tscn.
;
; Visual: deep-pit dark strip (underground, cosmetic only).

